byline.original: By RICK ROJAS and NOAH REMNICK

lead_paragraph: The girl, Natalia Jimenez, fell five stories and was pronounced dead at a Manhattan hospital.

headline.print_headline: Girl, 15, Dies After Fall From Midtown Roof
headline.main: Girl, 15, Killed in Fall From Rooftop in Hell’s Kitchen

snippet: The girl, Natalia Jimenez, fell five stories and was pronounced dead at a Manhattan hospital.
abstract: Fifteen-year-old Natalia Jimenez dies after attempting to jump from one rooftop to another in Hell's Kitchen neighborhood of Midtown Manhattan.
